1.0.0.changelog:
Initial release.
Note: CustomUILib is a required dependency, this mod will not work without CustomUILib being installed as well.

1.1.0.changelog:
Added:
- An option to tween color and colorX by HSV instead of RGB (disabled by default).
- An option to use unclamped lerp calculations (enabled by default).

Fixed:
- Back, elastic, and spring easing presets being clamped.

Note: CustomUILib is a required dependency, this mod will not work without CustomUILib being installed as well.
Built against Resonite version 2024.7.4.1347.

1.2.0.changelog:
Added:
- An option to enable/disable the mod.
- Error popup when the mod fails to initialize, such as in the case of CustomUILib not being available.

Updated:
- Code style & refactoring.

Fixed:
- Interpolating colors by HSV not underflowing their hue if the difference of hues is over 180°.

Removed:Escape Unicode Characters
- Being able to apply easing functions to non-lerpable types, such as booleans.

Note: CustomUILib is a required dependency, this mod will not work without CustomUILib being installed as well.
Built against Resonite version 2024.7.12.12.

owo.Nytra.ComponentSearchWizard.description: Adds a wizard to allow searching for components that exist on slots in the current world. You can search by type and/or by name, and get a list of references as output.
owo.Nytra.ComponentSearchWizard.name: ComponentSearchWizard

owo.Nytra.FixSessionBrowser.description: A mod that fixed the session browser. This is no longer needed as of Beta 2024.1.30.731.
owo.Nytra.FixSessionBrowser.name: FixSessionBrowser

owo.Nytra.HotReloadLib.description: Library for Resonite mod developers to hot reload their mods without needing to restart the whole game.
owo.Nytra.HotReloadLib.name: HotReloadLib

owo.Nytra.InspectorDelegateCaller.description: Adds some buttons to inspector UI for workers that have callable delegates.
owo.Nytra.InspectorDelegateCaller.name: InspectorDelegateCaller

owo.Nytra.LeftHandedProtoFlux.description: Makes ProtoFlux flow from right to left.
owo.Nytra.LeftHandedProtoFlux.name: LeftHandedProtoFlux

owo.Nytra.LogFlush.description: A mod primarily for developers that flushes the log stream when you press the F1 key, causing all buffered messages to be written to the log file.
owo.Nytra.LogFlush.name: LogFlush

owo.Nytra.NoTankControls.description: Don't lock up joystick movement while tools are equipped. Very helpful on Quest. This version has tweaks to work better with InspectorScroll.
owo.Nytra.NoTankControls.name: NoTankControls-InspectorScrollCompatible

owo.Nytra.ReferenceFinderWizard.description: Adds a wizard that lets you find references to things. Has options to adjust the search and can optionally spawn a detailed text output.
owo.Nytra.ReferenceFinderWizard.name: ReferenceFinderWizard

owo.Nytra.ScrollableFieldEditors.description: Allows clicking into inspector fields and then scrolling to change the value.
owo.Nytra.ScrollableFieldEditors.name: ScrollableFieldEditors

owo.Nytra.WorldListSessionHider.description: A mod that hides session info and thumbnails in your session browser based on the host's userID/username, the world ID or the session ID.
owo.Nytra.WorldListSessionHider.name: WorldListSessionHider

1.2.0.changelog: Added option to filter sessions out by world ID and improved config string parsing.

page.newweb.HeadlessTweaks.description: Adds some nice to have features to headless clients. To use the discord related options `Discord.Net.Webhook`, `Discord.Net.Rest`, and `Discord.Net.Core` libraries are required, view the readme for more information.
page.newweb.HeadlessTweaks.name: HeadlessTweaks

2.1.10.changelog:
- Fixed start world commands creating invalid invites
- Fix nml typo in a warning message fixed by XDelta

2.1.9.changelog:
- Added the option to automatically accept invite requests sent using the Ask to Join button (`AutoHandleInviteRequests`)
  - This will send an invite for whatever session the headless is currently focused on
  - This is only done if it is sent directly to the headless by the person requesting, this does not apply to forwarded requests
  - The permission check is handled the same as the `/reqInvite` command
  - If the user does not have permission to join then the request will be forwarded to the session admins

- Discord changes
  - Added `WorldCrashed` event
  - Added option to add go.resonite.com link to session start message (`DiscordLinkToSession`)
  
- Command changes
  - Added ability for `reqInvite` to do partial match
  - Stop `reqInvite` command from reporting full world name if you do not have permission to join
  - Fixed starting worlds with a world orb
  - Fixed start world commands not always reporting a name

- Misc changes
  - Exposed RegisterCommands as a public method
  - Updated project files

semmiedev.NoDoubleTapSprint.description: Disable double-tap sprinting when using a keyboard
semmiedev.NoDoubleTapSprint.name: NoDoubleTapSprint
